      • add

        <T> boolean add(String key,
                int expiration,
                Object value,
                SerializationType serializationType)
         throws TimeoutException,
                CacheException
        Add object to cache if it doesn't exist.
        Parameters:
        key - the key
        expiration - expiration time in seconds as defined in memcached specification
        value - the value to add
        serializationType - type of serialization
        Returns:
        true if a mutation has occurred (object didn't exist in cache)
        Throws:
        TimeoutException
        CacheException

      • getNativeClient

        Object getNativeClient()
        Expose native memcached client. Do not store reference to this client because it can change in runtime when using some feature (like runtime memcached nodes switching).
        Returns:
        current instance of native memcached client
        Since:
